'''蜜蚁'''（{{lang-en|'''Honey Ant'''}}），又稱之為'''蜜壺蟻'''或'''蜜罐蟻'''（'''Honeypot Ant'''），是{{link-en|蜜罐蟻屬|Myrmecocystus}}和[[弓背蚁属|弓背蚁属]]等幾屬[[螞蟻|螞蟻]]的統稱，最大特徵在於具有一種稱為貯蜜蟻（{{lang-en|'''repletes'''<ref>{{cite web |url=http://antbase.org/databases/glossary_files/glossary_QU.htm |title=Replete |publisher=Antbase |accessdate=30 July 2016 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303204122/http://antbase.org/databases/glossary_files/glossary_QU.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>, '''plerergates''', '''rotunds'''}}）的特殊階級，這些工蟻由其他工蟻[[食物|餵食]]直到其[[腹部|腹部]]脹滿，類似於{{link-en|貯藏室|larder}}。其他蟻群成員則能在食物缺乏時從這些貯蜜蟻取得[[營養學|營養]]。1881 年由{{link-en|亨利·C·麥庫克|Henry Christopher McCook}}首次記錄<ref>{{cite book |authorlink=Henry Christopher McCook |last1=McCook |first1=Henry C. |title=The Honey and Occident Ants |date=1882 |publisher=}}</ref><ref>{{cite book |authorlink=Henry Christopher McCook |last1=McCook |first1=Henry C. |title=Nature's craftsmen; popular studies of ants and other insects |date=1907 |publisher=Harper and Brothers |url=https://archive.org/details/naturescraftsmen00mcco |pages=96–111 }}</ref>，並於 1908 年由{{link-en|威廉·莫頓·惠勒|William Morton Wheeler}}正式發表<ref name=Wheeler1908/>。

== 行為 ==
許多昆蟲，尤其是蜜蜂與數種胡蜂，會收集並儲存蜂蜜在蜂巢中。而蜜罐蟻最特別的地方在於牠們演化出專門負責儲存糖蜜的貯蜜蟻階級。當需要食物時，工蟻會去碰觸貯蜜蟻的觸角，而貯蜜蟻就會將儲存在[[嗉囊|嗉囊]]的糖蜜反芻吐回來餵予工蟻<ref name=Wheeler1908>{{cite journal|last1=Wheeler|first1=William Morton|authorlink1=William Morton Wheeler|title=The Polymorphism of Ants|journal=Annals of the Entomological Society of America|date=March 1908|pages=39–69|doi=10.1093/aesa/1.1.39|url=http://aesa.oxfordjournals.org/content/1/1/39|access-date=2019-05-19|archive-date=2016-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160921034831/http://aesa.oxfordjournals.org/content/1/1/39|dead-url=no}} (subscription required)</ref><ref name=NG>{{cite web |title=Honey Ant Adaptations |url=http://nationalgeographic.org/media/honey-ant-adaptations-wbt/ |publisher=[[National_Geographic_Society|National Geographic]] |accessdate=30 July 2016 |archive-date=2021-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120124043/https://www.nationalgeographic.org/media/honey-ant-adaptations-wbt/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 解剖學 ==
[[File:Honey_Ants_(7344580116).jpg|thumb]]
部分蜜罐蟻如膨咕巨山蟻（''Camponotus inflatus''）的[[腹部|腹部]]由堅硬的{{link-en|骨片|sclerite}}與柔軟的關節膜所組成。當沒有儲存糖蜜時，關節膜會收摺並且使骨片重疊，外型就與一般螞蟻相差無異。而當腹部充滿糖蜜時，關節膜會完全撐開，使得骨片之間分離<ref name="GullanCranston2009">{{cite book |url={{google books |id=E_6-pGOLUgcC |pg=PA25 |plain-url=yes }}
